snippet.title: Station 37 official trailer
snippet.description:
Grab the free game here:
https://frankiesmileshow.itch.io/station-37
(the link in the video leads to some squatter fake blog site that took over after I stopped paying for my domain name)

Game by FrankieSmileShow (graphics, programming) and the Monster King (programming),
with music by Chef Boyardee

Thanks to Chef, Lurdiak and the Poppenkast for prompt testing/feedback/comments/etc before this was out.
